root: ^You` They may not be able to arrest Jake for murdering someone who is still alive, but he can still be tresspassed, I guess.

c-0: ^You` Reginald is smart enough to watch his back.
^You` I don't know what happened to everyone in that other world, but at least they won't be suffering anymore.
^You` To them it's just a day at the carnival, over and over again for the rest of time.
^You` I might not be able to save them, but maybe they don't need to be saved anymore.
^You` And the Jake that's stuck in that world will never be able to murder the Ring Master, because the Ring Master is here now. To them he doesn't even exist.
^You` Reginald might be alive now, but he'll probably keep treating his employees poorly. He's certainly not a hero.
^You` I'll be able to write up a puff piece for tomorrow, though I think I'll leave out a lot of the details.
^You` Now my life goes back to normal, and I pretend like nothing happened at all.
^You` I think I'm okay with that. I'm okay with things being normal, at least for a bit.
